features: PIZAS TOWER GAME PLUSHIES: Experience the thrill of popular game Pizas Tower with these highly detailed plushies. This plushies set includes 4 dolls: White Cook (100g, H:8.7inch/22cm, W:5inch/12.7cm) & Yellow Cook(115g,H:10.3inch/26cm, W:4inch/10cm) & Pizaface(110g, H&W: 8.7inch/22cm) & Pepperman(125g, H:10inch/25cm, W:6.5inch/16.5cm). Crafted from premium quality, soft pure PP Cotton, these dolls are hand-sewn to achieve a round and full appearance, free from any peculiar smell.

VERSATILE USAGE: These plushies are portable and perfect for taking with you to school, the park, or while traveling. They serve multiple purposes, such as game fan symbols, home decorations, pillow fight companions, artistic displays, and make great gifts for gamers, collectors, and special occasions like Christmas, Halloween, birthdays, Fathers' Day, Thanksgiving, and New Year's Day.

SOFT, SAFE, AND COMFORTING: Handmade with a pillow-like softness, these plushies are lightweight, gentle to touch, and provide warmth. They are safe for children to play with, ensuring the safety of your home and pets. Suitable for all ages, these adorable monster plushies are delightful to collect, trade, and surprise your friends, family, and kids.

WIDE SELECTION: This plushies set is suitable for ages 3+ and made from 100% safe materials to protect your children during playtime. They offer a comfortable and flexible feel, with a delicate texture that retains its shape. Our store offers a variety of game plushies to choose from, featuring vibrant colors that are easy to clean.
